org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.addressing.pdef
Class AePartnerAddressRef

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.addressing.pdef.AePartnerAddressRef
public class AePartnerAddressRef
extends java.lang.Object

This class models the mapping of a parnterLinkType and role to endpoint reference. In addition, it keeps track of the references to this mapping (as there may be more than one deployment using the same partner address mappings).
